<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="28Mar1918"><font color="red">ca. 28 February 1919</font>, <cite>JML</cite> (JJ to Ezra Pound): I am very sorry to hear you have had the Spanish influenza &hellip; I have been ailing all this year with my eyes but I hope in a few days to begin work again &hellip; I hope you received the episode of the Symplegades. That of Sirens will follow.</div>
